
@baseUrl = http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}
@v1 = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1

### Health
GET {{v1}}/health

### Get all users
GET {{v1}}/users

### Get a user by ID
GET {{v1}}/users/1

### Create a new user
POST {{v1}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "123123",
  "age": 30
}

### Update a user by ID
PUT {{v1}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "email": "john.doe.updated@example.com",
  "passwordHash": "new_hashed_password",
  "age": 31,
  "isActive": true
}

### Soft delete a user by ID
DELETE {{v1}}/users/1